OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with clear periods. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will remain dry
OL,8,Facross all parts with variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FThe morning will be dry and
OL,12,Fcloudy, but some brightness along the
OL,13,Fnorth coast. Rain will spread east in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon and evening. Mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA cold
OL,17,Fstart with some frost on Friday, then
OL,18,Fa dry and sunny day, Dry and bright on
OL,19,FSaturday, Cloudy with a chance of rain
OL,20,Fon Sunday.
